### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### Sign Up - New User
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "Test@123",
  "confirmPassword": "Test@123",
  "firstName": "New",
  "lastName": "User",
  "phoneNumber": "+1234567890"
}

### Sign In - Student Account
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student1@attendance.com",
  "password": "Student@123"
}

### Sign In - Instructor Account
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "instructor@attendance.com",
  "password": "Instructor@123"
}

### Sign In - Admin Account
POST http://localhost:3001/api/v1/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@attendance.com",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### Get Profile (Replace YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN with actual token from signin)
GET http://localhost:3001/api/v1/auth/profile
